50|$|To {{the west}} is <b>Coram's</b> Fields, a {{playground}} for children, and to the east is Gray's Inn Road, a major thoroughfare for the area. Goodenough College is a postgraduate residence and educational trust on {{the north and south}} sides of the square, and operates an academic-oriented hotel on the east side.|$|R
